snippet: Kevin Streelman finally won on the PGA Tour by shooting a four-under-par 67 in the final round in the Tampa Bay Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla.
abstract: Kevin Streelman wins golf's Tampa Bay Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla.
